headline: JPMorgan says Corteva split announcement has not lowered company’s value
summary: Investing.com -- Corteva’s plan to split into two companies has drawn a negative initial market reaction, but JPMorgan sees an opportunity, upgrading the stock to Overweight.

headline: Chemours (CC) Price Target Lifted by Mizuho Amid Higher Market Multiples
summary: The Chemours Company (NYSE:CC) ranks among the best specialty chemicals stocks to invest in. Mizuho maintained its Outperform rating on The Chemours Company (NYSE:CC) and raised its price target from $16 to $19 on September 23. The increase is mostly attributable to higher market multiples, as Mizuho used a higher multiple of roughly 6.5x next-twelve-months […]
